{"tid":1503322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遊行示威賽後檢討","createTime":"2019-08-25T02:51:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T16:16:38.000Z","uid":302558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7c8369cc576b28d818799a543aeca154e6c58e42","tid":1503322,"uid":302558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:51:04.000Z","msg":"利申：我係P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唔岩聽diu得細力d<br />\n琴日睇到勇武派心聲<br />\n堅持每個星期六日出黎想keep住大家道氣<br />\n我好明白勇武派既付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係我唔想再見到大家白白犧牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以勇武派每個星期只出一次<br />\n唔好出哂兩日呢？<br />\n其實一日都可以做到你地想要既效果同減少被捕人數<br />\n另一日可唔可以係純和理非活動<br />\n例如香港之路都好熱血好成功<br />\n<br />\n你地既決心同犧牲，你地已經成功表現出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以係時候檢討策略<br />\nkeep住兩日出黎唔係好既方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最緊要係捱到美國關注同救我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b7f9307622a1fe27c4f3f6cbb2f6b5cd0e916c1","tid":1503322,"uid":277263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:51:55.000Z","msg":"揸春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />揸春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />揸春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />揸春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />揸春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n揸春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />揸春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />揸春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />揸春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />揸春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳帆呼籲市民：寧願參加其他活動都好過堵塞機場<br />\n